##If you're setting up your company's first UK branch or subsidiary

You may be eligible for a [UK Expansion Worker visa (Global Business Mobility)](/uk-expansion-worker-visa) if you work for an overseas company and you're planning to set up your first UK branch or subsidiary.

###Eligibility

The eligibility criteria include:

- working in an eligible job
- being paid a minimum salary - how much depends on the type of work you do

